facts.seriesTitle: Prevalence rate of bribery (percent)
facts.fact_text: The prevalence rate of bribery was 6.2 % in 2010.

facts.seriesTitle: Proportion of firms experiencing at least one bribe payment request (percent)
facts.fact_text: The proportion of firms experiencing at least one bribe payment request declined from 14.7 % in 2009 to 7.5% in 2013.

facts.seriesTitle: Primary government expenditures as a proportion of original approved budget (percent)
facts.fact_text: Primary government expenditures as a proportion of original approved budget declined from 104.6 % in 2007 to 92.2% in 2017.

facts.seriesTitle: Proportion of children under 5 years of age whose births have been registered with a civil authority (percent)
facts.fact_text: In 2011, there were about 99.7 % of children under age 5 whose births were registered with a civil authority

facts.seriesTitle: Foreign direct investment (FDI) inflows (millions of dollars)
facts.fact_text: Foreign direct investment (FDI) inflows increased from 24.0 million dollars in 1994 to 737.1 million dollars in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Remittances in dollars as a proportion of total GDP (percent)
facts.fact_text: In 2018, the inflow of personal remittances was 2.7 % of GDP , up from 1.5 % in 1996

facts.seriesTitle: Debt service as a proportion of exports of goods and services (percent)
facts.fact_text: Debt service as a proportion of exports of goods and services increased from 5.0 % in 1996 to 6.6% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Fixed Internet broadband subscriptions (per 100 inhabitants)
facts.fact_text: Fixed-broadband internet penetration reached increased from 0.6 per 100 inhabitants in 2005 to 20.6 per 100 inhabitants in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Internet users  (per 100 inhabitants)
facts.fact_text: The number of Internet users per 100 inhabitants increased from 2.5 in 2000 to 79.2 in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Total official development assistance (gross disbursement) for technical cooperation (millions of 2018 dollars)
facts.fact_text: The total gross disbursement of official development assistance for technical cooperation in constant prices of 2018 stood at 87.2 million dollars in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, most-favoured-nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with most-favoured-nation status declined from 7.6 % in 2005 to 6.0% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with preferential status declined from 3.1 % in 2005 to 1.3% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Dollar value of all resources made available to strengthen statistical capacity in developing countries (million dollars)
facts.fact_text: The value of all resources made available to strengthen statistical capacity in developing countries was 25.3 million dollars in 2017.
